{"id": 1227, "date": "1987-03-01T11:00:18", "date_gmt": "1987-03-01T19:00:18", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=1227"}, "modified": "2026-06-09T13:18:23", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-09T20:18:23", "slug": "matr-bruce-springsteen-and-jimmy-fallon-sexy-and-i-know-it", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/03/01/matr-bruce-springsteen-and-jimmy-fallon-sexy-and-i-know-it/", "title": {"rendered": "Sexy and I Know It"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>To promote Bruce&#8217;s new\u00a0<em>Wrecking Ball\u00a0</em>album, Jimmy Fallon declared the last days of February 2012 and the first days of March as &#8220;Bruce Springsteen Week,&#8221; featuring interviews with and performances by the artist himself.</p>\n<p>Bruce did more than debut his own new material, though: he also spoofed himself by donning his 1980s uniform (and hair!) and joining Jimmy Fallon-as-Neil Young for an inspired cover of LMFAO&#8217;s &#8220;Sexy and I Know It.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wyx6JDQCslE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Here&#8217;s that brilliantly silly performance:</p>\n<div id=\"v-9ki7nHat-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/9ki7nHat?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>Sexy and I Know It<br />\nFirst performed:</strong> March 2, 2012 (New York City, NY)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> March 2, 2012 (New York City, NY)</p>\n<p>\u00a9 March 24, 2018</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>A self-spoofing Bruce joins Jimmy Fallon-as-Neil Young for a hilarious take on LMFAO&#8217;s &#8220;Sexy and I Know It.&#8221;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 69790, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_feature_clip_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [3617, 5], "tags": [52, 586, 585, 587], "class_list": ["post-1227", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-it-takes-two", "category-meeting-across-the-river", "tag-jimmy-fallon", "tag-lmfao", "tag-neil-youn", "tag-sexy-and-i-know-it"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/360295-120305-ent-fallon-springsteen.webp?fit=1000%2C660&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": true, "jetpack_shortlink": "https://wp.me/p9w3Lk-jN", "jetpack_likes_enabled": true, "jetpack-related-posts": [{"id": 12480, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/03/24/matr-bruce-springsteen-and-jimmy-fallon-whip-my-hair/", "url_meta": {"origin": 1227, "position": 0}, "title": "Whip My Hair", "author": "Ken", "date": "March 24, 1987", "format": false, "excerpt": "Bruce and Jimmy Fallon (as Neil Young) perform the unlikeliest of covers in one of Bruce's most viral moments. Watch the performance and backstory inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T134056.095.jpg?fit=1000%2C1000&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T134056.095.jpg?fit=1000%2C1000&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T134056.095.jpg?fit=1000%2C1000&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T134056.095.jpg?fit=1000%2C1000&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 37344, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2022/08/31/matr-rotd-bruce-springsteen-and-jimmy-fallon-gov-christie-traffic-jam/", "url_meta": {"origin": 1227, "position": 1}, "title": "MatR/RotD: Bruce Springsteen and Jimmy Fallon: Gov. Christie Traffic Jam", "author": "Ken", "date": "August 31, 2022", "format": false, "excerpt": "At the height of the Bridgegate scandal, Bruce reprised his 80s-era team-up with Jimmy Fallon to throw some shade Governor Christie's way.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Meeting Across the River&quot;", "block_contex